rows.label: qst200404_msg0001
rows.name:
A loan shark? You shouldn't
borrow money from that guy.

rows.label: qst200404_msg0002
rows.name:
He's in league with a
doctor named Celian.

rows.label: qst200404_msg0003
rows.name:
The doctor charges patients high medical
fees, and if they can't pay, he sends
them to his favorite loan shark...

rows.label: qst200404_msg0005
rows.name:
You all be careful not to
end up under Celian's care.

rows.label: qst200404_msg0101
rows.name: Be careful of that doctor, Celian.
